At the touch of love, everyone becomes a poet lol. True love is never blind but rather brings an added light... Love beyond what we think. As you watch and listen to this song "Whispers" by Prosper Menko, Get ready to feel a warm embracelike the warm morning sun on your face, so renewing, Refreshing, Life Giving, Comforting and a Blessing, This lets you know true love is here.
